modules.description: Provides functions to retrieve network connection status, including whether the device is online, the type of connection (wifi, cellular, etc.), and connection quality. Works with boolean flags, string identifiers, and structured data representing network states. Used to conditionally enable or disable features based on real-time network availability.

Provides functions to retrieve and convert network connection information. Works with a custom `connection` type representing device network status. Converts the current connection state to a string for display or logging purposes.
